OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FLegislation will be introduced to
OL,8,Fensure all young people in Northern
OL,9,FIreland remain in education or
OL,10,Ftraining until they are 18, Paul Givan
OL,11,Fhas told the Assembly.
OL,13,FThe Education Minister also said he
OL,14,Fwanted to begin a conversation on the
OL,15,Ffuture of qualifications in the
OL,16,Fregion, which he said needed to
OL,17,F"remain comparable with the rest of
OL,18,Fthe United Kingdom".
