OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Givan was delivering his
OL,8,Fdepartmental response to the
OL,9,Frecommendations and findings of the
OL,10,FIndependent Review of Education in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FThe report last year made 25 key
OL,14,Frecommendations, underpinned by a
OL,15,Ffurther 106 areas for action,
OL,16,Fincluding investment in early years
OL,17,Fprovision, reform of the curriculum
OL,18,Fand the qualifications system.
