OL,3,CYoung people to stay in education or
OL,4,Ctraining until 18, says Education
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Givan told MLAs on Monday he had
OL,8,Faccepted almost all of the
OL,9,Frecommendations.
OL,11,FHe said too many young people in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland affected by poverty
OL,13,F"continue to leave education both
OL,14,Funder-skilled and under-qualified".
OL,16,FThe minister said: "Subject to
OL,17,FExecutive agreement, I will legislate
OL,18,Fto ensure that all children remain in
OL,19,Feducation or training until they are
OL,20,F18 years old."
