OL,3,CYoung people to stay in education or
OL,4,Ctraining until 18, says Education
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FAt present, young people in Northern
OL,8,FIreland can leave school at the age of
OL,9,F16.
OL,11,FMr Givan added: "Participation in
OL,12,Feducation beyond the age of 16
OL,13,Fdirectly impacts upon life chances of
OL,14,Fyoung people.
OL,16,F"Regrettably, a young person's
OL,17,Fbackground remains a key factor in
OL,18,Fwhether they progress to post-16
OL,19,Feducation.
