OL,3,CYoung people to stay in education or
OL,4,Ctraining until 18, says Education
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"Compulsory education or training,
OL,8,Fending at 16, is a remnant of a
OL,9,Fmanufacturing society with many
OL,10,Funskilled jobs that no longer exists.
OL,12,F"Jobs today require high levels of
OL,13,Fskill and education.
OL,15,F"By mandating education or training
OL,16,Funtil 18, we can create a minimum
OL,17,Foffer for all young people,
OL,18,Fparticularly our most vulnerable."
