OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Givan continued: "This is a
OL,8,Fcommitment to our young people and our
OL,9,Ffuture and I ask all parties to work
OL,10,Fwith me to make it a reality."
OL,12,FThe minister said in the coming weeks
OL,13,Fhe would publish a strategy setting
OL,14,Fout his plans in detail for education
OL,15,Ftransformation.
OL,17,FHe said this would include reform in
OL,18,Fthe areas of assessment,
OL,19,Fqualifications and school improvements.
