OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHe told MLAs he had already
OL,8,Fcommissioned a curriculum review to
OL,9,Fexamine design and delivery and said
OL,10,Fthere would be a new literacy and
OL,11,Fnumeracy strategy for Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FThe minister also announced a review
OL,14,Fof arrangements to assess pupils'
OL,15,Fprogress throughout their time in
OL,16,Feducation.
OL,18,FHe also said he wanted to "begin a
OL,19,Fwide-ranging conversation on the
OL,20,Ffuture of our qualification system".
