OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Givan said: "We need to ensure
OL,8,Fqualifications are accessible, fit for
OL,9,Fpurpose, easily understood by pupils,
OL,10,Fparents and employers and remain
OL,11,Fcomparable with the rest of the United
OL,12,FKingdom.
OL,14,F"I will refine and improve
OL,15,Faccountability measures to remove
OL,16,Fperverse incentives for schools to
OL,17,Fenter pupils into low-value
OL,18,Fqualifications and instead reward
OL,19,Fschools for providing all pupils with
OL,20,Fa stretching curriculum."
