OL,7,FMr Givan said the Independent Review
OL,8,Fof Education in Northern Ireland had
OL,9,Fidentified an annual gap of #155
OL,10,Fmillion to address the per-pupil
OL,11,Ffunding gap with England and Wales and
OL,12,Fa further #136 million shortfall
OL,13,Frelated to higher levels of learners
OL,14,Fwith a statement of educational need.
OL,16,FHe said: "Real-term cuts over recent
OL,17,Fyears have had a lasting and
OL,18,Fdetrimental impact on our young
OL,19,Flearners.
