OL,3,CYoung people to stay in education or
OL,4,Ctraining until 18, says Education
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"I am determined to reverse the legacy
OL,8,Fof historic underfunding.
OL,10,F"Investment in the education sector is
OL,11,Fcrucial to building a prosperous and
OL,12,Fsustainable future.
OL,14,F"It is the foundation of all economic,
OL,15,Fsocial and political development.
OL,17,F"As an Executive and Assembly, we are
OL,18,Fnot just investing in the present but
OL,19,Fsecuring the future for generations to
OL,20,Fcome."
