OL,7,FHe added: "Education is the
OL,8,Fcornerstone of our society. It shapes
OL,9,Fthe future of all of our children, our
OL,10,Fcommunities and our economy.
OL,12,F"It is time to invest in a better
OL,13,Ffuture. Children and young people
OL,14,Fdeserve nothing less."
