OL,11,Fwarm words today and no concrete
OL,12,Fproposals.
OL,14,F"There was also not a single mention
OL,15,Fof integrated education, Irish medium
OL,16,Fschools or how the minister intends to
OL,17,Faddress issues around relationship and
OL,18,Fsexuality education (RSE) or
